PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FBut workers say the Supreme Court
OL,8,Fruling on the definition of a woman
OL,9,Fhas impacted access to services, with
OL,10,Fsome services now turning them away.
OL,12,FGiselle, 38, one of those helped by
OL,13,Fthe refuge, came to the UK from
OL,14,FThailand after her husband promised
OL,15,Fher a better life.
OL,17,FInstead, she says she was trapped in
OL,18,Fan abusive marriage - controlled,
OL,19,Fisolated and eventually left homeless.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
