FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FShe is originally from Brunei, a small
OL,8,Fnation on the island of Borneo where
OL,9,Fbeing transgender is illegal under
OL,10,FSharia law - punishments can include
OL,11,Fimprisonment, physical violence and,
OL,12,Fin extreme cases, death.
OL,14,FGiselle met her ex-husband in
OL,15,FThailand. She says after they married,
OL,16,Fhe forced her to hide her identity.
OL,18,F"He told me not to tell anyone I am a
OL,19,Ftrans woman... not even his family. He
OL,20,Fsaid after five years, then we could
OL,21,Ftell them," she said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"He was manipulating me. He started
OL,8,Fcontrolling everything."
OL,10,FHe monitored her phone, restricted her
OL,11,Findependence and made her feel
OL,12,Fincapable of making her own decisions.
OL,14,FThe abuse escalated. Giselle says he
OL,15,Fdemanded money to pay for bills, used
OL,16,Fthreats of eviction to control her and
OL,17,Fsexually coerced her.
OL,19,F"He would get angry when I didn't give
OL,20,Fmy body to him," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@XO]{D@AOU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"I remember thinking - this is my
OL,8,Fbody. I have the right to say no."
OL,10,FAfter a year and a half, she was
OL,11,Fthrown out of the home and spent six
OL,12,Fdays homeless before being referred to
OL,13,FLoving Me.
OL,15,FShe says arriving at the refuge was
OL,16,Flife-changing.
OL,18,F"Before, I felt like I was a slave.
OL,19,FNow I feel empowered," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@bO]zD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"I can make my own decisions... I have
OL,8,Ffound my voice again."
OL,10,FGiselle's experience is not unique.
OL,11,FSamuel, now 19, fled abuse from his
OL,12,Ffamily at just 18 after coming out as
OL,13,Ftrans.
OL,15,F"When I came out, it was met very
OL,16,Fbadly," he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@VO]wD@AOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"Gendering me correctly was a struggle
OL,8,Ffor them and seeing me as male. As a
OL,9,Ftrans person you can tell when someone
OL,10,Fsees you as the gender you are and
OL,11,Fwhen they don't and that was always a
OL,12,Fpoint of contention."
OL,14,FSamuel was physically and verbally
OL,15,Fabused for years and eventually
OL,16,Freached a breaking point.
OL,18,F"My body just gave up... it became
OL,19,Funtenable and my body was telling me
OL,20,Fto get out."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
