PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FAfter three weeks homeless, Samuel
OL,8,Fsecured a place at Loving Me.
OL,10,F"The refuge offers the perfect space
OL,11,Ffor me," he said.
OL,13,F"I can be who I want to be and be safe
OL,14,Ffor the very first time. It's a place
OL,15,Fwhere I can stop and breathe."
OL,17,FA 2023 study by Galop found that 56%
OL,18,Fof trans and non-binary people did not
OL,19,Fseek professional support for abuse.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@HO]uD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FBut Loving Me Chief Operating Officer,
OL,8,FMelissa Dee, says that figure may now
OL,9,Fbe even higher.
OL,11,FShe says the Supreme Court ruling on
OL,12,Fthe definition of a woman is affecting
OL,13,Fhow trans people access support - with
OL,14,Fsome services now turning them away.
OL,16,FIn April 2025, the UK Supreme Court
OL,17,Fruled that the legal definition of a
OL,18,Fwoman is based on biological sex, with
OL,19,Fjudges saying that the "concept of sex
OL,20,Fis binary".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"We are seeing an uptake in services
OL,8,Ffeeling they can't support trans or
OL,9,Fnon-binary people in refuge
OL,10,Faccommodation," she said.
OL,12,F"That means there are far fewer
OL,13,Foptions available."
OL,15,FFor Giselle and Samuel, the refuge has
OL,16,Fprovided more than just safety ` it
OL,17,Fhas given them a chance to rebuild
OL,18,Ftheir lives.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@OO]tD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
