PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,FSamuel has a message for others in
OL,8,Fsimilar situations: "If your whole
OL,9,Flife has been abuse, it seems
OL,10,Fimpossible to imagine anything other
OL,11,Fthan that and to imagine a future
OL,12,Fwhere you can be free and be yourself
OL,13,Fand you can make your own decisions
OL,14,Fand be your own person but it is
OL,15,Fabsolutely possible and never give up
OL,16,Fon that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
