FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774469469
OL,3,C'I feel empowered': Inside North
OL,4,CWest's first trans refuge for abuse
OL,5,Csurvivors
OL,7,F"Save and make money where you can and
OL,8,Flook into renting private rooms or
OL,9,Fanything you can do to get out. Make
OL,10,Fsure everything is well thought out
OL,11,Fbut ultimately don't give up."
OL,26,@sD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
